{
  "stem": "8569.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we're sitting there I don't know for how long.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when everything was finally quiet, we walked out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were the only ones left in that building, because they had found the bunker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took everybody out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're the only two left alive from this house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We run across the street, and my mother didn't hear what was going on, and she was safe, too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that point, my father-- you know, this idea of the workshop with the frames went.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was no longer valid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father registered as a wood carver.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as such, he got work in the German military cemetery, which was situated outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His job was to carve the names and the ranks of the fallen German soldiers, their date of birth, and the date if death on the crosses that were then put in the cemetery to mark their graves.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as such, he was working outside of the ghetto with a pass.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was able to bring from outside food, which was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had again bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Sometimes we had tomato, and potatoes, and whatever it is that he could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And with this pass, he was allowed to bring those things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this helped us in terms of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day, pass or no pass, my father was taken to Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Umschlagplatz was the place where all the Jews were gathered before being transported out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father's boss at that time was a German captain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I wish I knew his name, but I don't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my sister had his number, so she called him and told him what happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came immediately with his car to the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
